data.description: **Property currently listed at appraised value!** Country living with a short 20 minute drive to Holmen or Black River Falls. Gravel driveway gives way to a spot that has already been graveled and leveled off for construction of a new garage. Entry into the home brings you into the kitchen/dining area. Also on the main level is the living room, 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, laundry room and rear mud room. Upstairs you will find 3 more bedrooms and a bathroom. Accompanying the home is a 12x16 storage shed and 2.25 acres. For the outdoor enthusiast/avid hunter, enjoy a little over 1,100 acres of public land bordering your new property!
